---
title: Middle Eastern-Spiced Cauliflower Bowl with Rice, Peas & Cilantro-Cumin Yogurt Sauce
description: Bold, earthy spices flavor tender cauliflower and green peas in this quick, filling vegetarian bowl. Fluffy jasmine rice soaks up the savory spices while a tangy yogurt sauce, flavored with smoky cumin and fresh cilantro, is drizzled over the top for cool, creamy contrast. Crunchy almonds finish off this hearty, flavorful meal.
